data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath DR Horton home is on a corner lot and on a cul de sac!  Also incudes a gorgeous sparkling community pool and playground.  This 2 story home has 2 living areas, 2 dining areas, and a very large sequestered Primary Bedroom.  This home is meticulously clean and ready for new owners.  It is also available for rent now @ $3400 a month.
